'''海洋酸化'''（{{lang-en|Ocean acidification}}）指的是海洋吸收大氣中的二氧化碳後，pH值逐漸降低的趨勢，<ref name=cald03>{{Cite journal|author=K.Caldeira & M. E. Wickett |year=2003 |title=Anthropogenic carbon and ocean pH |url=http://pangea.stanford.edu/research/Oceans/GES205/Caldeira_Science_Anthropogenic%20Carbon%20and%20ocean%20pH.pdf |journal=Nature |volume=425 |issue=6956 |pages=365 |doi=10.1038/425365a |pmid=14508477 |bibcode=2001AGUFMOS11C0385C |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130919212524/https://pangea.stanford.edu/research/Oceans/GES205/Caldeira_Science_Anthropogenic%20Carbon%20and%20ocean%20pH.pdf |archivedate=2013-09-19 }}</ref>由於人類排放的二氧化碳中有約30%到40%會溶解於海洋、河流和湖泊等水體中<ref name=millero95>{{Cite journal |last=Millero |first=Frank J. |year=1995 |title=Thermodynamics of the carbon dioxide system in the oceans |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/001670379400354O |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924131319/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/001670379400354O |archivedate=2015-09-24 |journal=Geochimica et Cosmochimica Acta |volume=59 |issue=4 |pages=661–677 |doi=10.1016/0016-7037(94)00354-O |pmid= |bibcode=1995GeCoA..59..661M |access-date=2013-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Feely04>{{cite journal |last=Feely |first=R. A. |coauthors=''et al.'' |title=Impact of Anthropogenic CO<sub>2</sub> on the CaCO<sub>3</sub> System in the Oceans |journal=Science |volume=305(5682) |pages=362–366 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/content/305/5682/362.abstract |bibcode=2004Sci...305..362F |doi=10.1126/science.1097329 |date=July 2004 |access-date=2013-12-30 |archive-date=2013-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624132713/http://www.sciencemag.org/content/305/5682/362.abstract |dead-url=no }}</ref>
溶解的二氧化碳中，部分會和水生成碳酸，並電離出氫離子，導致海水的pH值降低，酸度升高。據研究者推測，從1751到1994年，海洋表層海水的pH值從8.25降低到了8.14<ref name=jacob05>{{cite journal | last=Jacobson | first=M. Z. | year=2005 | title=Studying ocean acidification with conservative, stable numerical schemes for nonequilibrium air-ocean exchange and ocean equilibrium chemistry | journal=[[Journal_of_Geophysical_Research|Journal of Geophysical Research]] – Atmospheres | volume=110 | doi=10.1029/2004JD005220 | url=http://www.agu.org/journals/ABS/2005/2004JD005220.shtml | pages=D07302 | bibcode=2005JGRD..11007302J}}</ref>，表示氫離子濃度幾乎增加了30%<ref name="pmid18536730">{{Cite journal |author=Hall-Spencer, J. M. |coauthors=Rodolfo-Metalpa, R.; Martin, S.; ''et al.'' |title=Volcanic carbon dioxide vents show ecosystem effects of ocean acidification |journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] |volume=454 |issue=7200 |pages=96–9 |pmid=18536730 |doi=10.1038/nature07051 |bibcode=2008Natur.454...96H|date=July 2008}}</ref><ref name="scor-int">{{Cite web |url=http://www.scor-int.org/OBO2009/A%26O_Report.pdf |title=Report of the Ocean Acidification and Oxygen Working Group, International Council for Science's Scientific Committee on Ocean Research (SCOR) Biological Observatories Workshop |accessdate=2020-09-13 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711050422/http://www.scor-int.org/OBO2009/A%26O_Report.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>海洋酸化和其他生物地理化學變化的綜合影響，都有可能破壞海洋生態系統的功能，對很多海洋物種產生危害<ref name="#1">{{cite journal |last1=Mora |first1=C. et al. |title=Biotic and Human Vulnerability to Projected Changes in Ocean Biogeochemistry over the 21st Century |journal=Plos Biology |volume=11 |pages=e1001682 |year=2013 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.1001682}}</ref>。

海洋酸化被認為具有一系列不良後果，比如抑制洪堡烏賊的新陳代謝速度<ref name=Rosa>{{cite journal |last=Rosa |first=R. |last2=Seibel |first2=B. |title=Synergistic effects of climate-related variables suggest future physiological impairment in a top oceanic predator |journal=P.N.A.S. |volume=105(52) |year=2008 |month= |pages=20776–20780 |url=http://www.pnas.org/content/105/52/20776.short |bibcode=2008PNAS..10520776R |doi=10.1073/pnas.0806886105 |access-date=2013-12-30 |archive-date=2014-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141206113108/http://www.pnas.org/content/105/52/20776.short |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[無孔貽貝|淡菜]]的免疫反應<ref name=Bibby>{{cite journal |last=Bibby |first=R. |coauthors=''et al.'' |title=Effects of ocean acidification on the immune response of the blue mussel Mytilus edulis |journal=Aquatic Biology |volume=2 |year=2008 |month= |pages=67–74 |url=http://www.int-res.com/abstracts/ab/v2/n1/p67-74/ |access-date=2013-12-30 |archive-date=2013-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110100808/http://www.int-res.com/abstracts/ab/v2/n1/p67-74/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>及加速[[珊瑚白化|珊瑚白化]]。海洋酸度增加還帶來了其他的化學反應，如碳酸根離子增加，會減緩珊瑚蟲和浮游生物等海洋生物的成鈣過程，已經形成的鈣質也更容易溶解。此外，海洋酸化對海洋食物鏈也帶來威脅。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/31/science/earth/31ocean.html |title=Rising Acidity Is Threatening Food Web of Oceans, Science Panel Says |author=Cornelia Dean |publisher=New York Times |date=January 30, 2009 |accessdate=2013-12-30 |archive-date=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130517195626/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/31/science/earth/31ocean.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author= Robert E. Service |title= Rising Acidity Brings and Ocean Of Trouble |journal=Science|pages= 146–148 |volume= 337 |date= 13 July 2012|bibcode = 2012Sci...337..146S }}</ref>

「聯合國氣候變化綱要公約」（UNFCCC）中，目前有105個國家承諾於2050年前達碳中和。

